@startuml 23-ask-from-contact
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Ask AI from Contact Detail

actor User
participant "ContactDetailPage" as CD
participant "AskModePage" as AM
participant "POST /api/ask (SSE)" as API

User -> CD: tap Ask AI (aAsk)
CD -> AM: navigate /ask?contactId={id}&seed=...
AM -> AM: input.set("What should I say to {name} next?")
AM -> AM: focus input
AM --> User: seeded input visible

User -> AM: (optional) edit text, tap Send
AM -> API: POST { question, contactId }
API -> API: bias retrieval toward contactId
API --> AM: SSE (token / citations / followups / done)
AM --> User: streaming answer\n+ mini-cards (likely incl. this contact)

@enduml
